        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin, neutral narrator"
        },
        "text": "蕭長老聞言，臉色驟變。隱藏等級——那只有大乘期以上的存在才有的標記！"
